data.description: Charming 2-story home with plenty of space and potential! A 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home with 2,093 sq. ft. offers ample room for a large family or for those who enjoy having extra space for guests, offices, or hobbies. The fact that it's a 1900s build adds character and possibly some unique architectural features. With an oversized corner lot and a fenced yard, you likely have plenty of outdoor space for various activities or even gardening. Centrally located just a few blocks from beautiful downtown Baker City!
